               <msContents>
                  <summary>Acts of Ewosæatewos; Eleven Miracles of Ewosṭatewos; Greeting to Ewosæatewos; Hymn to Ewosæatewos; Computus, Baḥǝrä Ḥasab, Calendar of Biblical Characters and Ethiopian Kings; Order of Monks; Monastic genealogy of the line of Abunä Ewosṭatewos; Image of Ewosṭatewos; Image of Ewosṭatewos</summary>
